Deprecated API

Contents

  • Deprecated Classes
  • Deprecated Methods
  • Deprecated Classes 
    Class and Description
    org.jlibsedml.Function
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    org.jlibsedml.SEDBase.addAnnotation(Annotation) 
    org.jlibsedml.SEDBase.addNote(Notes)
    From now on, setNote(Note note) should be used.
    org.jlibsedml.Annotation.getAnnotationElement()
    Use get getAnnotationElementList() from now on.
    org.jlibsedml.SEDBase.getNotes()
    Use getNote() from now on.
    org.jlibsedml.SEDBase.removeAnnotation(Annotation)
    Usr setAnnotation(null) from now on
    org.jlibsedml.SEDBase.removeNote(Notes)
    Use setNote(null) from now on, this method will have the same effect
    org.jlibsedml.SEDBase.setAnnotation(List<Annotation>)
    Use setAnnotation (annotation) - collections of Annotation are no longer supported.
    org.jlibsedml.SEDBase.setNotes(List<Notes>)
    Use setNote(Note n) from now on - this method will now just set the 1st element of the list.
    org.jlibsedml.Libsedml.writeSEDMLArchive(ArchiveComponents, String)
    - use OMEX /Combine archive format from now on - the sedx archive is obsolete.
